# 📘 Phase 11 — Multi-Format RAG System (Document Ingestion Upgrade)

## 🧭 Overview

Phase 11 upgrades the AI system from a basic PDF-only ingestion pipeline into a **multi-format, production-style RAG (Retrieval-Augmented Generation) system**.

The system now supports:
- Multiple document types (PDF, DOCX, TXT)
- Pluggable extraction architecture
- Metadata-aware embeddings
- Soft delete document management
- Persistent vector storage using ChromaDB
- Session-based AI chat with retrieval

